<template>
  <el-table
      :data="tableData"
      v-if="tableDataShow"
      style="width: 100%"
  >
    <el-table-column align="center" label="ID" width="100" type="index">
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="quartersThird"
        label="领域"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="enEndDate"
        label="截止日期"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="enterpriseName"
        label="公司名称"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="enRecentNumber"
        label="剩余招聘人数"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="rpPhase"
        label="招聘进度"
    >
    </el-table-column>


    <el-table-column
        label="操作"
        width="100">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-button @click="goto(scope.row)" type="text" size="small">查看详情</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {

}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
